{"tid":2217793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跨性別人士試穿運動內衣被拒　店員稱「需顧及其他女性觀感」","createTime":"2020-09-25T16:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T18:16:10.000Z","uid":325060,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d96f85dc71bf49b3a55adda440c14db316a1de","tid":2217793,"uid":325060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"跨性別人士試穿運動內衣被拒　店員稱「需顧及其他女性觀感」　 6IXTY8IGHT 道歉認員工處理失當<br />\n<br />\n一名完成性別重置手術、身分證顯示為女性的跨性別人士，今（25 日）在跨性別權益會陪同下到平機會投訴，稱連鎖內衣店 6IXTY8IGHT 上月拒絕她使用試衣室，懷疑是因自己仍有男性聲線遭拒。事主許小姐認為店員不容許她試身屬差別待遇，要求 6IXTY8IGHT 道歉，並促請平機會徹查；6IXTY8IGHT 回應稱，對涉事員工的處理失當深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/跨性別人士試穿運動內衣被拒-店員稱-需顧及其他女性觀感-6ixty8ight-道歉認員工處理失當/?fbclid=IwAR0IZi_V1qQHves0RYIWZi9K5DYMO7heAQxBHY1yfm4XTL_eKBvJDxmUgBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%B7%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A9%A6%E7%A9%BF%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1-%E9%9C%80%E9%A1%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%A7%80%E6%84%9F-6ixty8ight-%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E8%AA%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0IZi_V1qQHves0RYIWZi9K5DYMO7heAQxBHY1yfm4XTL_eKBvJDxmUgBY&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=882be56b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%B7%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E8%A9%A6%E7%A9%BF%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1-%E9%9C%80%E9%A1%A7%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E8%A7%80%E6%84%9F-6ixty8ight-%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E8%AA%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0IZi_V1qQHves0RYIWZi9K5DYMO7heAQxBHY1yfm4XTL_eKBvJDxmUgBY&h=5f555047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/跨性別人士試穿運動內衣被拒-店員稱-需顧及其他女性觀感-6ixty8ight-道歉認員工處理失當/?fbclid=IwAR0IZi_V1qQHves